<h2 class='date-header'><span>Wednesday, December 31, 2014</span></h2>

          <div class="date-posts">
        
<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='http://thumb9.shutterstock.com/display_pic_with_logo/450076/109778576/stock-photo-most-popular-stamp-109778576.jpg' itemprop='image_url'/>
<meta content='36405856' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='9116825170135146070' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='9116825170135146070'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://askakorean.blogspot.com/2014/12/most-popular-aak-posts-of-2014.html'>Most Popular AAK! Posts of 2014</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-9116825170135146070' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<div align="center">
<table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;"><tbody>
<tr><td style="text-align: center;"><img height="320" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/proxy/al333dsz1auJalOkAjTjIkoO58jgmV1HZxs5oVMZpOE7sPGM-bMCu_dP-RQmbglHgKMNXSOp4BUfHym_DqFpnBdn0ZbQvuZ2t0hHUd0hr3DVjg6V5RSeP2gdo-LlrGnaThx5PECFL3APRC_wjc1xzf8wCAIZgLlDNbadwSRTNKc8viRb-xM=s0-d" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width="305"></td></tr>
<tr><td class="tr-caption" style="text-align: center;">(<a href="http://thumb9.shutterstock.com/display_pic_with_logo/450076/109778576/stock-photo-most-popular-stamp-109778576.jpg">source</a>)</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br /></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
Here is a quick look back at the most popular AAK! posts of 2014, by the number of page view.<br />
<b><b><u><br /></u></b></b>
<b><b><u>Most Viewed Posts of 2014 (All-Time Posts)</u></b></b></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br />
1. &nbsp;<a href="http://askakorean.blogspot.com/2012/01/lose-weight-with-korean-diet-part-1.html">Lose Weight with Korean Diet</a></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
2. &nbsp;<a href="http://askakorean.blogspot.com/2008/09/ultimate-korean-looks-list-how-to-pick.html">The Ultimate Korean Looks List</a></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
3. &nbsp;<a href="http://askakorean.blogspot.com/2007/09/everything-you-ever-wanted-to-know.html">Everything You Ever Wanted to Know About Korean Men</a></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
4. &nbsp;<a href="http://askakorean.blogspot.com/2014/06/sweet-delicious-eff-you.html">Why did the Korean National Soccer Team Got Candies Thrown at Them?</a></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
5. &nbsp;<a href="http://askakorean.blogspot.com/2009/01/fan-death-is-real.html">Fan Death is Real&nbsp;</a></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br /></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
Weight loss, as it turns out, was the greatest thing that TK has ever written about.<br />
<b><b><u><br /></u></b></b>
<b><b><u>Most Viewed Posts of 2014 (Written in 2014)</u></b></b></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br />
1. &nbsp;<a href="http://askakorean.blogspot.com/2014/06/sweet-delicious-eff-you.html">Why did the Korean National Soccer Team Got Candies Thrown at Them?</a></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
2. &nbsp;<a href="http://askakorean.blogspot.com/2014/04/the-sewol-tragedy-part-i-accident.html">The Sewol Tragedy: Part I - The Accident</a></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
3. &nbsp;<a href="http://askakorean.blogspot.com/2014/05/the-sewol-tragedy-part-ii-causes-and.html?spref=tw">The Sewol Tragedy: Part II - Causes and Contributing Factors</a></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
4. &nbsp;<a href="http://askakorean.blogspot.com/2014/08/what-makes-good-korean-restaurant.html">What Makes a Good Korean Restaurant?</a></div>
<div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
5. &nbsp;<a href="http://askakorean.blogspot.com/2014/05/the-sewol-tragedy-part-iii-fallout.html">The Sewol Tragedy: Part III - The Fallout</a></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br /></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
The sinking of the Sewol ferry was the defining event of Korea for this year, and this blog's readership reflected that.&nbsp;</div>
</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br /></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
TK already has one new year's resolution: blog more often. I have been quite negligent with AAK! this year--especially in the second half of the year. There were great stories about Korea that gathered international attention, such as the Nut Gate, KC Royals Super Fan, etc., that TK could hardly catch up to. In 2015, TK will reduce other commitments and redouble his effort on AAK!</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br /></div>
<div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
The Korean wishes everyone a warm and happy end of the year. As always, thank you for reading this humble blog. See you next year.</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<br /></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
<i>Got a question or a comment for the Korean? Email away at</i> askakorean@gmail.com.</div>
</div>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
</div>
